/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時男人唔覺淡左 開心見誠講啦 再唔係絲打pm我等我安慰下妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918bad3de262c75fef493ebc2a3c48e1896716c4","tid":26463,"uid":25776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人係會突然有一日同你講感覺淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咪係女人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男人都會突然同你講分手之後失蹤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講分手夜晚都可以失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時男人唔覺淡左 開心見誠講啦 再唔係絲打pm我等我安慰下妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打 我同我男朋友半年 我一直對佢好冷淡 直到呢幾日發生左事 原來佢有同第個曖昧 但正正因為咁 我發現原來冷淡係行唔通 真正同佢傾過先知大家有好多誤會 依家解決左 所以好好同你男朋友傾下"},{"pid":"28d8d3ea3c921a14aa0ced0d20af2154b8a7ddd8","tid":26463,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人係會突然有一日同你講感覺淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咪係女人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男人都會突然同你講分手之後失蹤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講分手夜晚都可以失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時男人唔覺淡左 開心見誠講啦 再唔係絲打pm我等我安慰下妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打 我同我男朋友半年 我一直對佢好冷淡 直到呢幾日發生左事 原來佢有同第個曖昧 但正正因為咁 我發現原來冷淡係行唔通 真正同佢傾過先知大家有好多誤會 依家解決左 所以好好同你男朋友傾下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日有時間都想接佢放工見多佢幾面... 因為我同佢根本見得唔多，又唔會成日出去拍拖...<br />\n但每一次我話想去接佢既時候，佢都唔想... 其實我都唔怕走黎走去，都只係想見到佢，那怕只係一程地鐵都好呀...<br />\n有時好多野都想同佢講，但係見面果時講唔出，電話除左溝我果陣會同我傾之外一齊之後都冇幾可會聽我電話，send whatsapp佢又唔會同我認真講野，日頭返工夜晚又返打機，根本唔知可以點同佢講..."},{"pid":"1d9a717b9fc311050dfcc89c5408fbded4a6cfc1","tid":26463,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人係會突然有一日同你講感覺淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咪係女人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男人都會突然同你講分手之後失蹤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講分手夜晚都可以失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時男人唔覺淡左 開心見誠講啦 再唔係絲打pm我等我安慰下妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打 我同我男朋友半年 我一直對佢好冷淡 直到呢幾日發生左事 原來佢有同第個曖昧 但正正因為咁 我發現原來冷淡係行唔通 真正同佢傾過先知大家有好多誤會 依家解決左 所以好好同你男朋友傾下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日有時間都想接佢放工見多佢幾面... 因為我同佢根本見得唔多，又唔會成日出去拍拖...<br />\n但每一次我話想去接佢既時候，佢都唔想... 其實我都唔怕走黎走去，都只係想見到佢，那怕只係一程地鐵都好呀...<br />\n有時好多野都想同佢講，但係見面果時講唔出，電話除左溝我果陣會同我傾之外一齊之後都冇幾可會聽我電話，send whatsapp佢又唔會同我認真講野，日頭返工夜晚又<span style=\"color: red;\">話</span>打機，根本唔知可以點同佢講...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61be1a450921a5dc8c115f0704f3a5839b60ee90","tid":26463,"uid":38800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始同自己講唔好諗咁多，最後到我覺得忍得好辛苦，要坦白講嘅時候就係分手嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我相信會遇到個珍惜我嘅人，所以而家每一日都同自己講唔可以灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2e7332e3cdb8a0a1976aa0a5fd389b6f6d85d0","tid":26463,"uid":52546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"5726e58ef91e7ef4546c35cd6c0bf9be6b20995e","tid":26463,"uid":25776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人係會突然有一日同你講感覺淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咪係女人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男人都會突然同你講分手之後失蹤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講分手夜晚都可以失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時男人唔覺淡左 開心見誠講啦 再唔係絲打pm我等我安慰下妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打 我同我男朋友半年 我一直對佢好冷淡 直到呢幾日發生左事 原來佢有同第個曖昧 但正正因為咁 我發現原來冷淡係行唔通 真正同佢傾過先知大家有好多誤會 依家解決左 所以好好同你男朋友傾下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日有時間都想接佢放工見多佢幾面... 因為我同佢根本見得唔多，又唔會成日出去拍拖...<br />\n但每一次我話想去接佢既時候，佢都唔想... 其實我都唔怕走黎走去，都只係想見到佢，那怕只係一程地鐵都好呀...<br />\n有時好多野都想同佢講，但係見面果時講唔出，電話除左溝我果陣會同我傾之外一齊之後都冇幾可會聽我電話，send whatsapp佢又唔會同我認真講野，日頭返工夜晚又<span style=\"color: red;\">話</span>打機，根本唔知可以點同佢講...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係男朋友接我我都唔想見 同埋好小見面 一星期一次 因為我成日好忙 忙完又累 想留係屋企 之後我自己成日上網睇戲唔理佢 搞到件事發生左 之後我約左佢出黎傾 先發現原來佢覺得我陪得佢太小 又好似唔想認佢係我男朋友  又好多好多誤會 <br />\n你不如同佢講 我地出黎傾下 你問下佢覺唔覺大家有咩問題 如果佢話冇 你咪開始引入先 你問下有冇野要變 如果佢都話冇 咁你放棄呢段感情喇"},{"pid":"32e1c0f4a6fe5103bef47b595c5cb227e0feec29","tid":26463,"uid":44982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"獌聯和波啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0befe50f354752526ede82ed33b2021835f6aa7b","tid":26463,"uid":50413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"c3cd85851d21ec7088741644ea79195d41d5df24","tid":26463,"uid":16128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人係會突然有一日同你講感覺淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咪係女人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男人都會突然同你講分手之後失蹤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗講分手夜晚都可以失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊左幾耐？<br />\n係咪嘈過交？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇嘈交 半年都未到<br />\n不過我又鐘意亂諗野<br />\n希望係我亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h